# Digitizing telecom assets into a shared pool

## Use case description
The digitization of telecom assets and their transformation into a shared pool offers numerous benefits. It promotes cost efficiency by reducing individual investments and streamlines deployment for broader network coverage. Blockchain technology enhances transparency, security, and collaboration among operators, ensuring seamless asset sharing and management while supporting the adoption of innovative technologies like 5G.

## Companies applying this use case
[Weaver Labs](https://www.weaverlabs.io/)

